      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "RUN ROLEX (1) is a handy type who notched her 4th career success when too good (30.78) from Box 2 at this track. The form out of the last run is proven to be strong. Looks the testing material. SIMPLICITY MAGIC (2) boasts a strong record this course with seven wins and five minors from 19 tries. Hit the frame latest (34.61) when third at The Gardens in a Grade 4/5. With even luck and a clean start can sneak into the finish. OXLEY FLYER (8) has performed well at her last couple of runs here, most recently when third beaten 2.5 lengths (30.57). Goes well this circuit with four wins and two minors. Will give a great sight again. HURRY TUNCURRY (3) deserves plenty of thought over this distance.",
